<li>loadFromSQL fixed</li>
<li>loadFromSQL IDs fix</li>
<li>Current Fluent Literal update</li>
<li>&quot;NOW&quot; fixed for all databases</li>
<li>InsertIntoSQL returns Integer now</li>
<li>Package description filled correctly</li>
<li>insertToSQL now handle createColumn content if not set</li>
<li>deleteFromSQL() work again</li>
</ul>

