            'title' => 'php-ease-core 1.47.0 released',
            'text' => '<div class="release-info d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
  <img src="img/deb/php-ease-core.png" alt="php-ease-core" style="height:48px;object-fit:contain;flex-shrink:0">
  <div>
    <h4 class="mb-0">php-ease-core</h4>
    <span class="badge bg-secondary">1.47.0</span>
  </div>
</div>
<h2>[1.47.0]</h2>
<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Added function <code>isUuid()</code> (b32c2d6)</li>
<li><code>Functions::writeResult</code> added (b5dc16e)</li>
<li><code>Molecule::setFloatProperty()</code> added. UnitTests for Molecule updated (9102e26)</li>
<li>Molecule tester added to dev package (2dae34c)</li>
<li>SandTester added to dev package (2c733fd)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>setupBoolProperty</code> now can handle bool properties (3ce8580)</li>
<li><code>writeResult</code> is now a static function (d9899a0)</li>
<li>Shared test update (4a2ca14)</li>
<li>Use <code>EMAIL_FROM</code> as sender name fallback (1944fc7)</li>
<li>Mailer does not fail when <code>Pear_Error</code> occurs (9507709)</li>
<li>Singleton for Loggers update (40b69e4)</li>
<li>Code updates using PHPStan (b9d9e86)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>loadClassesInNamespace</code> fix for nonexistent psr4 autoloader (2cb9b3a)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Deprecated</h3>
<ul>
<li>Temporary disable phpdoc (a028455)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Removed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Do not build for bullseye &amp; focal (97e4df0)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/VitexSoftware/php-ease-core/compare/1.45.0...1.47.0">https://github.com/VitexSoftware/php-ease-core/compare/1.45.0...1.47.0</a></p>

