    <span class="badge bg-secondary">v0.2.0</span>
  </div>
</div>
<h1>igdebi v0.2.0 - Modern Debian Package Installer</h1>
<p> <strong>Major Release</strong> with updated dependencies, enhanced security, and improved user experience!</p>
<h2> What\'s New</h2>
<h3>✨ Enhanced Features</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Real-time Progress Bars</strong>: Beautiful download progress with speed indicators and ETA</li>
<li><strong>Modern Dependencies</strong>: Updated to latest stable versions (tqdm 4.67.0+, validators 0.20.0+, requests 2.25.0+)</li>
<li><strong>Enhanced Security</strong>: Replaced <code>os.system()</code> with secure <code>subprocess.run()</code> execution</li>
<li><strong>Better Error Handling</strong>: Comprehensive error messages and user guidance</li>
<li><strong>Keyboard Interrupt Support</strong>: Clean Ctrl+C handling with proper cleanup</li>
</ul>
<h3> Improvements</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Auto Cleanup</strong>: Downloaded files are automatically removed after installation</li>
<li><strong>URL Validation</strong>: Enhanced URL validation and file type checking</li>
<li><strong>Python 3.7+ Support</strong>: Modern Python support with proper type hints</li>
<li><strong>Better User Feedback</strong>: Clear status messages throughout the process</li>
</ul>
<h3> Development Tools</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Test Suite</strong>: Comprehensive testing with <code>test_igdebi.py</code></li>
<li><strong>Examples</strong>: Interactive examples with <code>examples.py</code></li>
<li><strong>Documentation</strong>: Complete README with usage examples and API reference</li>
<li><strong>Makefile</strong>: Development automation for common tasks</li>
</ul>
<h2> Installation</h2>
<h3>From Release (Recommended)</h3>
<pre><code class="language-bash">wget https://github.com/VitexSoftware/igdebi/releases/download/v0.2.0/igdebi_0.2.0_all.deb
sudo dpkg -i igdebi_0.2.0_all.deb
</code></pre>
<h3>From Repository</h3>
<pre><code class="language-bash">sudo apt install lsb-release wget
echo &quot;deb http://repo.vitexsoftware.cz $(lsb_release -sc) main&quot; | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/vitexsoftware.list
sudo wget -O /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/vitexsoftware.gpg http://repo.vitexsoftware.cz/keyring.gpg
sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo apt install igdebi
</code></pre>
<h2> Usage Examples</h2>
<h3>Download and Install from URL</h3>
<pre><code class="language-bash"># Install Apache NetBeans IDE
sudo igdebi https://github.com/Friends-of-Apache-NetBeans/netbeans-installers/releases/download/v27-build1/apache-netbeans_27-1_amd64.deb
</code></pre>
<h3>Install Local Package</h3>
<pre><code class="language-bash">sudo igdebi /path/to/package.deb
</code></pre>
<h2>�� Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>OS</strong>: Debian, Ubuntu, or derivatives</li>
<li><strong>Python</strong>: 3.7 or higher</li>
<li><strong>Dependencies</strong>: python3-tqdm, python3-validators, python3-requests, gdebi-core</li>
</ul>
<h2> Security</h2>
<p>This release includes important security improvements:</p>
<ul>
<li>Secure subprocess execution instead of shell injection risks</li>
<li>Proper input sanitization and validation</li>
<li>Enhanced error handling to prevent information disclosure</li>
</ul>
<h2> Testing</h2>
<p>Verified with real packages including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Apache NetBeans IDE (621MB)</li>
<li>Various system packages</li>
<li>Local .deb file installation</li>
</ul>
