<ul>
<li><strong>Changed property visibility</strong> to private for better encapsulation (except parent class requirements)</li>
<li><strong>Improved return type declarations</strong> (mixed instead of incorrect int/bool)</li>
<li><strong>Constructor now accepts optional $firma parameter</strong></li>
<li><strong>Refactored constructor logic</strong> into <code>loadByUsername()</code> and <code>loadByEmail()</code> helper methods</li>
<li><strong>Improved error handling</strong> with proper status messages throughout</li>
</ul>
<h3>➕ Added Features</h3>
<ul>
<li>Added <code>setFirma()</code> and <code>getFirma()</code> accessor methods</li>
