<li>Critical test added for getUserEmail() null handling</li>
</ul>
<h3>⚠️ Breaking Changes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Properties changed from public to private (use getter/setter methods)</li>
<li>Constructor signature accepts optional $firma parameter</li>
</ul>
