<h2>What\'s New</h2>
<h3>New Storage Backends</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Kafka</strong> — produces webhook changes as JSON messages to per-evidence topics via <code>php-rdkafka</code></li>
<li><strong>Redis Streams</strong> — stores changes in Redis Streams keyed by evidence type via <code>php-redis</code></li>
<li><strong>MongoDB</strong> — stores changes in per-evidence collections via <code>php-mongodb</code></li>
</ul>
