<td>Concentric circles pulsing with frequency bands</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4</td>
<td>Circular Spectrum</td>
<td>64 radial bars in a circle</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>5</td>
<td>Plasma</td>
<td>Animated colored blobs</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6</td>
<td>Starfield</td>
<td>Stars flying outward, speed scales with audio</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>7</td>
<td>Fireworks</td>
<td>Particle bursts on bass beats</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>8</td>
<td>Matrix Rain</td>
<td>Falling green characters</td>
</tr>
<tr>
