<td>DNA Helix</td>
<td>Two intertwined sine strands</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>10</td>
<td>Particle Storm</td>
<td>150 particles in audio-reactive orbits</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>11</td>
<td>Ripple Effect</td>
<td>Expanding concentric rings</td>
</tr>
<tr>
