<p>Analytics and reporting tool for <strong>Money S3 / Pohoda</strong> accounting systems, generating periodical digests in Markdown, HTML, and PDF formats.</p>
<hr />
<h3>What\'s included</h3>
<p><strong><code>pohoda-digest</code></strong> — the core package:</p>
